    "Clinic, Whole Health visits, nutrition appointments, and use of metformin or weight-loss medications.",
    "These findings suggest that virtual DPP enrollment rates were similar among women Veterans with and without prior use of VA preventive services.",
    "Thus, virtual DPP may fill an existing gap for women Veterans who have never previously engaged in VA preventive services as well as those who have previously engaged in VA-based preventive services.",
    "We also found that women Veterans with housing instability were significantly less likely to enroll in virtual DPP.",
    "To our knowledge, we are the first study to assess the association between housing instability and DPP enrollment."
